The format of VerbKB JSON file:

id: 0								(id of the verb)
verb: have							(the verb)
count: 63							(number of verb’s type signatures)
pattern:							(the list of type signatures)
	id: 0							(id of type signature)
	subject: location					(the subject type)
	verb: have						(the verb)
	objec: location						(the object type)
	expressions:						(the list of relations that the verb expresses)
		id: 0						(id of the relation)
		express: locationHaveLocation			(the relation)
		confidence: 0.85				(the confidence that the verb expresses the relation)
	count: 1.47						(the % of times the verb occurs in ClueWeb with the type signature)
	text:							(the top-20 actual mentions of the typed verbs in the ClueWeb corpus)
		id: 0						(id of the mention)
		subject: location:trip advisor			(the subject of the mention)
		verb: have					(the verb)
		objec: location:reviews				(the object of the mention)
		count: 25363					(the number of times this Subject-Verb-Object triple is mentioned in ClueWeb)

